Marx Brothers [1933] Duck Soup

The small state of Freedonia is in a financial mess, borrowing a huge sum of
cash from wealthy widow Mrs. Teasdale. She insists on replacing the current
president with crazy Rufus T. Firefly and mayhem erupts. To make matters worse,
the neighboring state sends inept spies Chicolini and Pinky to obtain top secret
information, creating even more chaos! 

Starring: The Marx Brothers: Groucho, Harpo, Chico and Zeppo

Director: Leo McCarey
